erts\", \"from\": 209, \"to\": 216}, {\"ngram\": \"unique items\", \"from\": 254, \"to\": 266}, {\"ngram\": \"members\", \"from\": 278, \"to\": 285}, {\"ngram\": \"the public\", \"from\": 289, \"to\": 299}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ever-knowledgeable Russell was taken aback when veteran journalist Gavin Bell presented an Olympic torch, having not anticipated such an iconic item would emerge from the day's collection.\", \"from\": 302, \"to\": 494, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 325, \"end\": 332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.4750542327811154e-12, \"text\": \"Russell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4964182\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\"}, {\"begin\": 373, \"end\": 383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gavin_Andresen\", \"score\": 0.9999999999881766, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gavin Bell\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gavin_Andresen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gavin_Andresen\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an Olympic torch\", \"from\": 394, \"to\": 410}, {\"ngram\": \"such an iconic item\", \"from\": 435, \"to\": 454}, {\"ngram\": \"the day's collection\", \"from\": 473, \"to\": 493}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With astonishment, Russell said: \\\"Before I came here today to the Roadshow, I had a long list of items in my head that I thought I might see that would appear out of boxes and bags in front of me.\", \"from\": 496, \"to\": 692, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 515, \"end\": 522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.4750542327811154e-12, \"text\": \"Russell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4964182\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"astonishment\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 513}, {\"ngram\": \"the Roadshow\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 570}, {\"ngram\": \"a long list\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 589}, {\"ngram\": \"items\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 598}, {\"ngram\": \"my head\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 609}, {\"ngram\": \"boxes\", \"from\": 662, \"to\": 667}, {\"ngram\": \"bags\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 676}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 680, \"to\": 685}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But one of them was definitely not an Olympic torch.\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 747, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an Olympic torch\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 746}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I wonder if you can tell us how you came to own this.\\\"\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 802, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 775}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bell, with a hint of nostalgia, recounted his journey: \\\"When I was a young lad, I was an 800 metres runner with a Glasgow club.\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 931, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 918, \"end\": 925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"score\": 0.9999999889419088, \"rank\": 9.893734241465468e-09, \"text\": \"Glasgow\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bell\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 808}, {\"ngram\": \"a hint\", \"from\": 815, \"to\": 821}, {\"ngram\": \"nostalgia\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 834}, {\"ngram\": \"his journey\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 857}, {\"ngram\": \"a young lad\", \"from\": 871, \"to\": 882}, {\"ngram\": \"an 800 metres runner\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 910}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So, of course, as a boy, I dreamed of running in the Olympics one day.\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 1004, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 947}, {\"ngram\": \"a boy\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 957}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 995}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And then eventually, the dream came true in a way I'd never have expected.\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1079, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the dream\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1035}, {\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1054}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was posted to South Korea in advance of the 1988 Games for The Times.\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1153, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1098, \"end\": 1109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.9999998870991994, \"rank\": 7.242706882437084e-08, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"advance\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1120}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1988 Games\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1138}, {\"ngram\": \"The Times\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1152}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And so while I was there, I met a couple of young English lads who'd been appointed to do the public relations for the torch relay.\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1285, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a couple\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1194}, {\"ngram\": \"young English lads\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1216}, {\"ngram\": \"the public relations\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1264}, {\"ngram\": \"the torch relay\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1284}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And they found out about my athletic background and invited me to carry the torch on the first day it arrived in Korea.\\\"\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1401, \"end\": 1406, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korea\", \"score\": 0.5701383184518048, \"rank\": 0.7467963226981411, \"text\": \"Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korea\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my athletic background\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1335}, {\"ngram\": \"the torch\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1369}, {\"ngram\": \"the first day\", \"from\": 1373, \"to\": 1386}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 1414, \"to\": 1523, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your sign-up\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1433}, {\"ngram\": \"content\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1452}, {\"ngram\": \"ways\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1460}, {\"ngram\": \"our understanding\", \"from\": 1498, \"to\": 1515}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1600, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"adverts\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1548}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1556}, {\"ngram\": \"3rd parties\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1572}, {\"ngram\": \"our understanding\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1599}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1633, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any time\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1632}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy Bell quipped that the snap of him holding the torch was \\\"good publicity\\\" for the Olympics and even landed on the front page of The Times.\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1795, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1785, \"end\": 1794, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Times\", \"score\": 0.9999999913413831, \"rank\": 8.658578074481453e-09, \"text\": \"The Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Times\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy Bell\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1661}, {\"ngram\": \"the snap\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1683}, {\"ngram\": \"the torch\", \"from\": 1699, \"to\": 1708}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"good publicity\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1728}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1746}, {\"ngram\": \"the front page\", \"from\": 1766, \"to\": 1780}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Russell expressed his delight, saying: \\\"I mean, it's fantastic.\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1860, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1797, \"end\": 1804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.4750542327811154e-12, \"text\": \"Russell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4964182\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his delight\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1826}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it's really amazing to see one here in rainy Glasgow.\", \"from\": 1861, \"to\": 1918, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1910, \"end\": 1917, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"score\": 0.9999999889419088, \"rank\": 9.893734241465468e-09, \"text\": \"Glasgow\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And what's also great is not only do we know from how it looks what it is but it tells us right here.\\\"\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 2023, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2008, \"to\": 2010}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He pointed out the inscription, which revealed the torch's journey from Olympia, Greece to the Olympic Stadium in Seoul in 1988.\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2153, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2097, \"end\": 2112, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia,_Greece\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Olympia, Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia,_Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.